{"tid":2005778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長洲覆核王自爆欠5000萬元訟費 遭律政司申請破產","createTime":"2020-05-07T10:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T10:37:43.000Z","uid":50740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bae188635d5401d07e5a735ffabda67ff7ea4058","tid":2005778,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅近年不斷與政府打官司，並且屢次敗訴，他前年接受傳媒訪問時，聲稱自己欠下政府5000萬港元訟費。律政司昨(6日)代表政府入稟高院提出呈請，要求法庭頒令郭卓堅破產。司法機構網頁顯示，案件將於7月8日在高院訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅前年向傳媒透露自己欠下政府巨額訟費，並表明自己「有錢畀」，更指該些訟費問題「唔使理」。他說：「最多咪宣布破產」，並笑稱「最好爭夠1億(港元)，可登上世界紀錄大全。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E6%B4%B2%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E7%8E%8B%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E6%AC%A05000%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%A8%9F%E8%B2%BB-%E9%81%AD%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%A0%B4%E7%94%A2-083149914.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E7%258E%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25AC%25A05000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25A8%259F%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E7%2594%25A2-083149914.html&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdQDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=9bf1d24c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E6%B4%B2%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E7%8E%8B%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E6%AC%A05000%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%A8%9F%E8%B2%BB-%E9%81%AD%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%A0%B4%E7%94%A2-083149914.html</a>"},{"pid":"5f18fdec29b6cd662b7a5de495d8f2880980ebce","tid":2005778,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"破左產申請法援仲方便左"},{"pid":"8dd336744a25f917f370a7d322bfb8973da49a3b","tid":2005778,"uid":168567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"人人都可以係覆核王"}]}